cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper involves the use of deep learning techniques such as CNN and LSTM for pattern recognition in stock data, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of CNN suggests that computer vision techniques may also be involved (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) for the pattern recognition task. Finally, the paper may also involve information retrieval techniques (cs.IR) for building the training set.
